data.description: **Priced for a quick sale!** Immaculate 3rd floor condo in The Reserve at James Island! This bright, 2 bedroom/2 bath unit features vaulted ceilings that accentuate the open concept living area. You will love the waterfront views from both bedrooms and the large private balcony. Each bedroom offers an en suite bathroom and oversized, walk in closets. The kitchen is equipped with newer stainless steel appliances. Off of the kitchen, you will find a separate laundry room with washer and dryer included. The meticulously maintained community offers Resort Style amenities, fitness room, basketball court, and plush landscaping. Located in the heart of Jacksonville, you are minutes from the Town Center shopping and amazing restaurants, UNF and only 9 minutes to the beaches. Home also comes with a 32 sq ft storage unit conveniently located on the ground floor with plenty of space for bikes. Schedule a showing today!
